&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Product Master Data&lt;/strong&gt; - Complete product information management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Stock Control Parameters&lt;/strong&gt; - Inventory management settings&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Multi-Location Support&lt;/strong&gt; - Warehouse and location-based inventory&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Pricing Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Cost and selling price configuration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Category Management&lt;/strong&gt; - Product classification and organization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
