&lt;li&gt;Detailed product specifications and descriptions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product images and multimedia attachments&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Multiple product codes (SKU, UPC, manufacturer code)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Product attributes and variants (size, color, model)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Technical specifications and documentation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supplier information and lead times&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
